    <item>
      <title>卢拉呼吁盟友马杜罗在委内瑞拉举行公平选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/lula-calls-on-ally-maduro-to-hold-fair-elections-in-venezuela</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦呼吁尼古拉斯·马杜罗领导的委内瑞拉政府在7月举行公平的总统选举，并表示没有任何理由排除本周无法报名参加竞选的反对派候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/lula-calls-on-ally-maduro-to-hold-fair-elections-in-venezuela</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 19:46:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列最高法院冻结神学院经费，令政府不安</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/israel-s-top-court-freezes-seminary-funding-rattling-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列最高法院下令政府从下周开始冻结数百所宗教神学院的资金，这对依赖极端正统政党的总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的执政联盟来说是一个意外打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/israel-s-top-court-freezes-seminary-funding-rattling-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 19:33:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙新总理任命萨尔门托为财政部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/portugal-s-new-premier-picks-sarmento-as-finance-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙即将上任的总理任命若阿金·米兰达·萨门托为财政部长，让他负责政府的财政政策，该政府没有获得多数席位，无法确保预算获得批准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/portugal-s-new-premier-picks-sarmento-as-finance-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 18:48:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德克萨斯州采取措施终止利润丰厚的休斯顿收费公路合同</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/texas-takes-step-to-terminate-lucrative-houston-tollway-contract</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州监管机构采取措施终止 Actividades de Construccion y Servicios SA 持有的 52 年收费公路特许经营权，并恢复对该州的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/texas-takes-step-to-terminate-lucrative-houston-tollway-contract</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 17:45:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦被要求调查一家弹药制造商的销售问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/yellen-asked-to-probe-security-issues-in-ammunition-maker-s-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院国土安全委员会成员、众议员克莱·希金斯 (Clay Higgins) 要求财政部长珍妮特·耶伦 (Janet Yellen) 在向捷克共和国一家公司出售美国弹药制造商的提议中“彻底审查国家安全问题”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/yellen-asked-to-probe-security-issues-in-ammunition-maker-s-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗正在测试拜登公平选举协议的极限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/maduro-tests-limits-of-biden-administration-s-fair-election-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗公然无视他对自由公正选举的承诺，哥伦比亚和巴西的盟友公开谴责他镇压反对派。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/maduro-tests-limits-of-biden-administration-s-fair-election-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
